
install angular : npm install -g @angular/cli
install angular material : ng add @angular/material
start app : ng serve

json : 
1 : npm install -g json-server
2 : json-server --watch db.json
create dialog componant: ng g c dialog
create api servce : ng g s services/api


-------------------

get/post products in : api.services.ts

add products func in : dialog.componant.ts

fetch products in : app.componants.ts

filter in : app componanats.ts

display products in : app.componants.ts

edit products in : app.componants.ts

display data inthe edit prompt we add a module (MAT_DIALOG_DATA) and inject it in the constructor in : dialog.componanats

to update/delete apicreated tani in : api.servce.ts 

refresh after update .afterClosed().subscribe(val=>{...}) in : app.componants.ts

delete methode in : app.componants.ts
